title: Memories On TV v4.0.4 Patched, Fully working!
description:
- unrar the downloaded rar file
- install memories on tv v4.0.4 
- restart computer 
- paste patch into program file ( mostly c:\program files\MemoriesOnTV4 )
- run the patch
- open memories on tv v4.0.4
- start the keygen and fill in a email address and push on generate
- copy the email and the serialcode
- you have a fully registered MOTV v4.0.4 pro

greetings from SW
